/#
   A collection of spot FX rates used in pricing.
 #/
record FpML5.recordkeeping.FxRateSet {
  # A collection of instruments used as a basis for quotation.
  instrumentSet : list< FpML5.recordkeeping.InstrumentSet >?

  # A collection of valuations (quotes) for the assets needed in the set. Normally these quotes will be for the underlying assets listed above, but they don't necesarily have to be.
  assetQuote : FpML5.recordkeeping.BasicAssetValuation?

}

instrumentSet.Doc: A collection of instruments used as a basis for quotation.
instrumentSet.Name: instrumentSet

assetQuote.Doc: A collection of valuations (quotes) for the assets needed in the set. Normally these quotes will be for the underlying assets listed above, but they don't necesarily have to be.
assetQuote.Name: assetQuote
